<title>USA: Crystal Systems to offer 1.2 mln shrs.</title>
<headline>Crystal Systems to offer 1.2 mln shrs.</headline>
<dateline>NEW YORK 1997-07-22</dateline>
<text>
<p>Crystal Systems Solutions Ltd said Tuesday the public offering of 1.2 million of its ordinary shares was priced at $27.00 per share.</p>
<p>The company will sell 600,000 ordinary shares, and certain shareholders are to sell 600,000 ordinary shares.</p>
<p>The company said it has granted the underwriters a 30-day option to buy up to 180,000 additional shares from certain shareholders to cover overallotments, if any.</p>
<p>The lead manager for the offering is UBS Securities and the co-managers are Oppenheimer &amp; Co Inc and Hampshire Securities Corp.</p>
